reviewText:
This has got to be the absolute worst movie ever made... The music was overbearing and dominated the entire "film." I've seen better acting in third rate Grammar school productions not that anyone would be able to act that unfocused and Ignorant so called script or what ever that was supposed to be...

Don't waste your time or money on this monstrous turd. Doesn't even rate one star but had to give it something.
Edit: other than the title on the cover... Nothing in the image has anything to do with the content.
